-- European Stocks Decline for Fourth Day as BP Leads Energy Shares Lower
-- Andrew Rummer
-- 2010-06-25T08:31:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-25/european-stocks-erase-their-earlier-advance-bp-drags-energy-shares-lower.html

          
          
             European stocks declined for a
fourth day as BP Plc dragged energy shares lower. The Stoxx
Europe 600 Index dropped 0.3 percent to 249.07 at 9:28 a.m. in
London, having earlier risen as much as 0.5 percent.  
          
          


  


        